#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an4.48"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.48:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.48:0.2"
msgid "5. Rohitassavagga "
msgstr "5. With Rohitassa "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.48:0.3"
msgid "48. Visākhasutta "
msgstr "48. With Visākha "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an4.48:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: pañcālaputto → pañcāliputto (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "an4.48:1.2"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena āyasmā visākho pañcālaputto upaṭṭhānasālāyaṃ bhikkhū dhammiyā kathāya sandasseti samādapeti samuttejeti sampahaṃseti, poriyā vācāya vissaṭṭhāya anelagalāya atthassa viññāpaniyā pariyāpannāya anissitāya. "
msgstr "Now at that time Venerable Visākha, Pañcāli’s son, was educating, encouraging, firing up, and inspiring the mendicants in the assembly hall with a Dhamma talk. His words were polished, clear, articulate, expressing the meaning, comprehensive, and independent. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.48:1.3"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā sāyanhasamayaṃ paṭisallānā vuṭṭhito yena upaṭṭhānasālā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā paññatte āsane nisīdi. "
msgstr "Then in the late afternoon, the Buddha came out of retreat and went to the assembly hall. He sat down on the seat spread out, "

msgctxt "an4.48:1.4"
msgid "Nisajja kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi: "
msgstr "and addressed the mendicants, "

#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an4.48:2.1"
msgid "“Ko nu kho, bhikkhave, upaṭṭhānasālāyaṃ bhikkhū dhammiyā kathāya sandasseti samādapeti samuttejeti sampahaṃseti poriyā vācāya vissaṭṭhāya anelagalāya atthassa viññāpaniyā pariyāpannāya anissitāyā”ti? "
msgstr "“Mendicants, who was educating, encouraging, firing up, and inspiring the mendicants in the assembly hall with a Dhamma talk?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.48:2.2"
msgid "“Āyasmā, bhante, visākho pañcālaputto upaṭṭhānasālāyaṃ bhikkhū dhammiyā kathāya sandasseti samādapeti samuttejeti sampahaṃseti poriyā vācāya vissaṭṭhāya anelagalāya atthassa viññāpaniyā pariyāpannāya anissitāyā”ti. "
msgstr "“Sir, it was Venerable Visākha, Pañcāli’s son.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an4.48:3.1"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā āyasmantaṃ visākhaṃ pañcālaputtaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then the Buddha said to Visākha, "

msgctxt "an4.48:3.2"
msgid "“sādhu sādhu, visākha. "
msgstr "“Good, good, Visākha! "

msgctxt "an4.48:3.3"
msgid "Sādhu kho tvaṃ, visākha, bhikkhū dhammiyā kathāya sandassesi samādapesi samuttejesi sampahaṃsesi poriyā vācāya vissaṭṭhāya anelagalāya atthassa viññāpaniyā pariyāpannāya anissitāyāti. "
msgstr "It’s good that you educate, encourage, fire up, and inspire the mendicants in the assembly hall with a Dhamma talk, with words that are polished, clear, articulate, expressing the meaning, comprehensive, and independent. "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an4.48:4.1"
msgid "Nābhāsamānaṃ jānanti, "
msgstr "Though an astute person is mixed up with fools, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.48:4.2"
msgid "missaṃ bālehi paṇḍitaṃ; "
msgstr "they don’t know unless he speaks. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.48:4.3"
msgid "Bhāsamānañca jānanti, "
msgstr "But when he speaks they know, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.48:4.4"
msgid "desentaṃ amataṃ padaṃ. "
msgstr "he’s teaching the deathless state. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "an4.48:5.1"
msgid "Bhāsaye jotaye dhammaṃ, "
msgstr "He should speak and illustrate the teaching, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.48:5.2"
msgid "paggaṇhe isinaṃ dhajaṃ; "
msgstr "holding up the banner of the hermits. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.48:5.3"
msgid "Subhāsitadhajā isayo, "
msgstr "Words well spoken are the hermits’ banner, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.48:5.4"
msgid "dhammo hi isinaṃ dhajo”ti. "
msgstr "for the teaching is the banner of the hermits.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.48:5.5"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
